headline: UFC® and Monster Energy® Announce Historic Renewal of Their Global Partnership
summary: LAS VEGAS, February 12, 2025--UFC®, the world’s premier mixed martial arts organization and part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), together with Monster Energy, the energy drink icon, today announced a multiyear renewal of their long-standing partnership in which Monster will continue to serve as the exclusive global Official Energy Drink of UFC.
